Esta es la Secta Qingyuan.

00:27:43.080 --> 00:27:44.080
Soy Cui Chen.

00:27:44.720 --> 00:27:45.360
Bien.

00:27:45.520 --> 00:27:47.360
Soy tu maestro, Qing Zhufeng.

00:27:48.120 --> 00:27:48.920
Saludos, Maestro.

00:27:49.440 --> 00:27:50.680
No hay necesidad de eso. Por favor levántate.

00:27:54.360 --> 00:27:55.440
Eres Zhao Tantan.

00:28:00.400 --> 00:28:01.440
Soy Zhao Tantan.

